1	Use the mouse to move the avatar
2	As soon as the game starts, you will see the colour you have to aim for on the top left corner
3	Names of colours in different colours will start dropping from the top of the window
4	You must touch only the ones that match either the name or the colour of the aimed one
5	You score if you touch the correct one
6	You lose a life and points if you touch the incorrect one or if you miss the correct one
7	On the top right corner is the remaining lives and current score
8	The game is over when all 3 lives are lost
9	You may submit your score by typing your name and clicking SEND or pressing ENTER
10	While playing the game or when the game is over, press ESC anytime to go back to the game menu 